I'm now considering the user's intent. Perhaps they want "Atlas Mode" as a top-level option in the quiz configuration, alongside "Exam" and "Study." This would mean moving the "Diagrams Only" filter out of the "Filters" modal. I'm checking `types.ts` for existing `AppMode`, focusing on `AppMode.ATLAS` for browsing. If I add a fourth card for "Atlas", it would set the state to diagram mode. I'm reexamining the original data manipulation context to see if there is a bug.


